&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an enthusiastic individual to work within our busy Ophthalmology Department at The Royal Free London Trust. The successful candidate will be highly motivated and be able to work independently and as part of a team. Attention to detail and the ability to work to strict quality and performance deadlines is essential. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The successful candidate is required to be able to demonstrate Trust values and meet the responsibilities of the job description and person specification. If you believe you meet the criteria and would like to join the Royal Free London at this time, we would be interested in receiving your application.&lt;/p&gt;
